    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine is strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are functioning as intended. While there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes such as small stone chips on the hood and light wear on the driver's seat bolster, the interior is clean and smoke-free. It has a complete service history and is ready for its next owner to drive with confidence.",
